<p>Well there are a lot of things. This is an old world item, and no required or recomended levels. You get those HP at any level. I THINK Stamina works like wis and int? The higher the level the more pool you get from it? Meaning you might not see the full bonus of stamina, where as the HP show up right away. Unfortunately there is a pretty heavy tide of change in MANA and HP items for power leveling new characters. That and super high end stuff. Rarity has a lot to do with it also.</p>
